/static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/166422697/image_166422697.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743912-14-upcoming-dividend-increases", "pub_date": "2024-12-12 19:35:46"}, {"id": "4743794", "title": "Super Micro Computer: Recovery Isn't Over Yet", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1828680033/image_1828680033.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Supermicro headquarters in San Jose, California, USA\" data-id=\"1828680033\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1828680033/image_1828680033.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1828680033/image_1828680033.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1828680033/image_1828680033.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1828680033/image_1828680033.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1828680033/image_1828680033.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1828680033/image_1828680033.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1828680033/image_1828680033.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1828680033/image_1828680033.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">JHVEPhoto</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2><span>Supermicro: Buyers Returned With Conviction</span></h2> <p>Investors in Super Micro Computer, Inc. (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/SMCI\" title=\"Super Micro Computer, Inc.\">SMCI</a></span>) who bailed and fled as the stock crashed below the $20 level, are now likely regretting their rash decision. Accordingly, SMCI has recovered more than 160% from its November 2024</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1828680033/image_1828680033.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743794-super-micro-computer-stock-recovery-isnt-over-yet", "pub_date": "2024-12-12 19:30:00"}, {"id": "4743918", "title": "Allspring Short-Term Bond Plus Fund Q3 2024 Commentary", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2166858256/image_2166858256.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Bonds word icon virtual screen with coins stacked in increasing stacks. Bonds increasing concept, investment bond concept Raising Funds to Fund the Green Bond Program.\" data-id=\"2166858256\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"864px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2166858256/image_2166858256.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2166858256/image_2166858256.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2166858256/image_2166858256.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2166858256/image_2166858256.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2166858256/image_2166858256.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2166858256/image_2166858256.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2166858256/image_2166858256.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2166858256/image_2166858256.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"></p> <p class=\"item-credits\">rawintanpin/iStock via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Quarterly review </h2> <p>The fund outperformed its benchmark, the Bloomberg U.S. 1\u20133 Year Government/Credit Bond Index, for the three-month period that ended September 30, 2024. Duration, quality, and sector allocation were the largest contributors to performance, followed by issue selection. Curve positioning detracted from performance</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2166858256/image_2166858256.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743918-allspring-short-term-bond-plus-fund-q3-2024-commentary", "pub_date": "2024-12-12 19:20:00"}, {"id": "4743916", "title": "Allspring Short Duration Government Bond Fund Q3 2024 Commentary", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1430785838/image_1430785838.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Businessman writing notes in documents model on stack of coins, in business, saving money\" data-id=\"1430785838\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1430785838/image_1430785838.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1430785838/image_1430785838.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1430785838/image_1430785838.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1430785838/image_1430785838.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1430785838/image_1430785838.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1430785838/image_1430785838.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1430785838/image_1430785838.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1430785838/image_1430785838.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"></p> <p class=\"item-credits\">ridvan_celik</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Quarterly review </h2> <p>The Bloomberg U.S. 1\u20133 Year Government Bond Index returned 2.89% for the third quarter of 2024. Front-end U.S. Treasury yields were significantly lower over the quarter as the market prepared for the first rate cut. The 2s/5s curve was 30 basis</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1430785838/image_1430785838.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743916-allspring-short-duration-government-bond-fund-q3-2024-commentary", "pub_date": "2024-12-12 19:10:00"}]}